window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>New York Times</i> best-selling author Simon R. Green’s novels featuring field agent Edwin Drood have won a devoted fan following. </p> <p>The Drood Matriarch has been murdered, exposing the family to powerful, evil factions and throwing the world into turmoil. A Satanic presence is growing, and although Edwin has always been something of an outsider, he’ll have to rise to the occasion to help thwart the menace and save his people.</p>"; 
